<span style="color: rgb(0, 170, 255);">What are the side effects?</span><br></span></h2><p class="sc-hYQoXb koTnzq pf-80_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hGnimi cpnKBf pf-82_">Depending on the type of doggie downer your vet prescribed, the side effects may differ for each specific drug. 
<br>
<br>Here are some known side effects for the type of drugs listed in the earlier section.
<br></span></p><div class="sc-igXgud kxFdJE pf-83_ pf-table-bordered" data-pf-type="Table"><table><tbody><tr><th class="A1"><span>Drug Type</span></th><th class="B1"><span>Common Side Effects</span></th><th class="C1"><span>Serious Side Effects</span></th></tr><tr><td class="A2"><span>Antidepressants</span></td><td class="B2"><span>Decreased appetite<br>Diarrhea<br>Excessive panting<br>Hypersalivation<br>Incoordination<br>Restlessness<br>Shaking<br>Sleepiness<br>Vomiting<br>Weight loss<br>Whining <br></span></td><td class="C2"><span>Aggression<br>Excessive vomiting<br>Seizures <br></span></td></tr><tr><td class="A3"><span>Anipryl </span></td><td class="B3"><span>Anorexia
